</row>
<row valign="top">
<entry align="left">4</entry>
<entry align="left">fjórflötungur (<emphasis effect="italics">d</emphasis><sup>0</sup> eða <emphasis effect="italics">d</emphasis><sup>10</sup>), lág oxunarástönd fyrir M</entry>
<entry align="left">[Ni(CO)<sub>4</sub>]</entry>
</row>
